{"tid":578774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"LINE推出「讓位」推播　孕婦上車立刻提醒你","createTime":"2018-03-03T03:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T13:25:53.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d0dc424284c34f89e53db70021d1b8b7495fa3f1","tid":578774,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:12:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/12142856/f04a7bdefedfc39e3a1e4d520f17c3fb_927770edf1fa8ce376c1c7bd8248e617.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F12142856%2Ff04a7bdefedfc39e3a1e4d520f17c3fb_927770edf1fa8ce376c1c7bd8248e617.png&h=6270443d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n日本東京地鐵一位難求，對需要座位的孕婦來說更是頭痛！通訊軟體LINE和東京地鐵合作，推出讓位對話群組，使用者和孕婦只要登入按下按鈕，有孕婦上車就會自動推播，提醒你讓位。<br />\n<br />\n東京地鐵和LINE合作，推出「讓位對話群組」，孕婦和使用者只要事先登入按下按鈕，系統就會自動推播讓座訊息。系統發想者說，有時看電車裡多數乘客們總是沉於手機世界，根本不會有人注意到孕婦，存在讓座率低的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/fun/834960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Ffun%2F834960&d=XljCogtkTx4Br8yDmcJzDQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=c58bebfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/fun/834960</a>"},{"pid":"15779556ac905ed08f2f628f503db31d0a264089","tid":578774,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:13:46.000Z","msg":"一旦手機出現通知，低頭族用戶也不必抬頭找人，只要回傳所在位置，配對過程不會外洩個人資料；另外還有這款「發送器掛飾」，輕按發亮找出好心讓座人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/_data/i/upload/2017/12/12/20171212201223-619683a7-me.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2F_data%2Fi%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F20171212201223-619683a7-me.jpg&h=fa3a40d5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n而南韓LINE則是推出智慧喇叭，讓可愛的LINE主人翁化身智慧助理，內建Clova智慧雲端不只能放音樂、播新聞，就連傳Line打電話也是直接用「說」的就好。Naver公關經理說，使用者透過揚聲喇叭的要求，累積形成多樣的大數據，透過這些大數據和Naver的內容結合，預計將會推出更新服務。"},{"pid":"cfcdb8698337ad0a5646647c35452ff8f325b008","tid":578774,"uid":165077,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"玩手機扮睇唔到都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a058065ead1353d4caecd43c996b11f659cf037","tid":578774,"uid":5891,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:23:33.000Z","msg":"line越出越多無謂嘢，由本身佢岩岩hit果陣推薦畀朋友用，到而家我已經hide notification,一個月先開嚟check一次(有極少數台灣朋友用佢嚟keep contact)<br />\n事關佢搞埋哂好似wechat果啲朋友圈咁嘅嘢，佢搞唔緊要喎，唔好成日都彈通知嚟話邊個邊個update左啦，我根本唔想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要冇得揀唔彈朋友圈嘅通知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嬲嬲地成個app嘅通知都hide撚哂佢"},{"pid":"c74f7ab86fb215288f748ff4c622f3267c2c5ba7","tid":578774,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"日本東京地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好等班垃圾廢青專登唔讓坐"},{"pid":"f74d8365f9592f933266fbe36af583eb9650ecd6","tid":578774,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:26:03.000Z","msg":"唔抬頭就係想扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e141f41a26583d4949067269954185927b9a350","tid":578774,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c74f7ab86fb215288f748ff4c622f3267c2c5ba7","tid":578774,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"日本東京地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好等班垃圾廢青專登唔讓坐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:29:36.000Z","msg":"英國都有<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/23173805/148516428334121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F23173805%2F148516428334121.jpg&h=716e7a3d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n英國倫敦有應用程式開發商，於當地時間今日推出一個方便孕婦的手機應用程式（App），希望她們可在乘搭交通工具，尤其是地鐵時，利用該程式向附近的路人發出提示，要求讓座。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/200858/英國開發商推孕婦讓座收費app%E3%80%80收入全數捐慈善機/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F200858%2F%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%95%86%E6%8E%A8%E5%AD%95%E5%A9%A6%E8%AE%93%E5%BA%A7%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BBapp%25E3%2580%2580%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E5%85%A8%E6%95%B8%E6%8D%90%E6%85%88%E5%96%84%E6%A9%9F%2F&d=XljCogtkTx4Br8yDmcJzDQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=a356cac0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/200858/英國開發商推孕婦讓座收費app%E3%80%80收入全數捐慈善機/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報道，此計劃名為「Babee on Board」（嬰兒在車上），是由當地應用程式開發商10x設計並推出。使用者需事先於手機上安裝「要求讓座」或「提供座位」的App：前者需收費3.99英鎊（即約38.5港元），孕婦可在需要座位時用；而後者則是免費的，予願意讓座的人士下載。報道引述應用程式開發商的行政總裁Hew Leith解釋，收費是想避免人們濫用該App，致孕婦不能真正受惠。他補充，公司所收取的費用將全數捐到當地慈善機構「Project Healthy Children charity」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，兩個Apps主要採用藍牙定位技術，用家即使在手機無訊號或WIFI的情況下，都可使用。Leith續指，現時大家只要一進入車廂內，就埋頭玩手機，根本不會留意到身邊發生的事，「只要孕婦在App中按下『讓座』按鈕，附近15英尺範圍內有安裝『提供座位』的人士就會收到信息提示」，「操作就如對講機般方便。」"},{"pid":"cc63a8d7c1e29e5c6f3661259e7183ff307214c5","tid":578774,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"廢老唔識用電話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5201cbcdab0a2f8e703965880e70c0d624fa1300","tid":578774,"uid":38316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:36:36.000Z","msg":"簡直係黑社會"},{"pid":"e08aab2c3c0c7f19b44c60ecae906426a71d47b9","tid":578774,"uid":81150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"我屌你架？<br />\n搵你老公讓啦仆街！"},{"pid":"e0ee4220f5e32ba540644c87f347bf91461ed68d","tid":578774,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"仲惡過"},{"pid":"e34e902e08c54132050aaeab4253975684c77ac0","tid":578774,"uid":173250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:50:01.000Z","msg":"香港快D推出"},{"pid":"8521869e3022d6255ef27764d48d4c7639784887","tid":578774,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:51:16.000Z","msg":"又唔䀠老夫有得關愛中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a22e45ecf930d2cfe5c39992681d2294fec74c9","tid":578774,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:51:33.000Z","msg":"日本人妻咁撚淫<br />\n可以趁機識返個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59679128dac14011bc8415be75037c47c71852b","tid":578774,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:54:52.000Z","msg":"為咗R位坐，無所不用其極"},{"pid":"ebdbf9675ba259e9b7e8194f600a1b2c3b020f51","tid":578774,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:56:33.000Z","msg":"又唔係我內射你 點解要讓？？<br />\n怪你老公要你大肚仲搭地鐵咁撚廢仲好啦<br />\non9"},{"pid":"c15b94953640a45b6b0cab4cc18f0beaac466bb9","tid":578774,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5201cbcdab0a2f8e703965880e70c0d624fa1300","tid":578774,"uid":38316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:36:36.000Z","msg":"簡直係黑社會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:59:06.000Z","msg":"真心反智 強逼讓座"},{"pid":"6031f7d1bae156b7a77ac72404b007d863ebc890","tid":578774,"uid":14203,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:01:22.000Z","msg":"讓比孕婦又冇乜所謂 廢老就不了"},{"pid":"4ad9efa84caf413bf63566d19997b22858f47584","tid":578774,"uid":1067,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:14:36.000Z","msg":"問吓中出你個位點解無的士，私家車坐&hellip;<br />\n點解要人地讓俾你坐？人地返咗成日工，晨早又要起身返工，你瞓係床度happy完啦，爽完啦，D精流曬出嚟啦，行到邊都摸吓自已個肚就要人讓你，你話你有無良知，知唔知個醜字點寫架？"},{"pid":"98c3669337a0ccba67fd69ef83f8e53b0689dd90","tid":578774,"uid":29551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:33:48.000Z","msg":"好聲好氣講句唔該我唔信你會無位坐，想人幫你但係咁簡單都唔肯做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af61d8bc62181da4d49739037365b5322a25675","tid":578774,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T11:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1563e149470c70027d901d10128eb3bb9bb6b260","tid":578774,"uid":81052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"見過有大肚婆搭火車<br />\n佢唔會扶住條柱,兩隻手係度禁電話<br />\n但之後聽到佢講電話呻冇人讓座<br />\n<br />\n自己都唔驚跌親,又想人讓座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa73690c34a226170633e52ee0958038013b0752","tid":578774,"uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T12:28:35.000Z","msg":"Line呢個垃圾app幾時先肯收皮？<br />\n<br />\n1.功能多到亂咁整<br />\n<br />\n2.效能極低，旗艦機都LAG<br />\n<br />\n3.垃圾廣告message/通知/群組<br />\n<br />\n4.安全性低<br />\n<br />\n5.BUG多到戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n日本人整既hardware我好欣賞，但software就真係不敢恭維"},{"pid":"397ec6961ff9e274d6f71c1cf8467ad613a8acc8","tid":578774,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa73690c34a226170633e52ee0958038013b0752","tid":578774,"uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T12:28:35.000Z","msg":"Line呢個垃圾app幾時先肯收皮？<br />\n<br />\n1.功能多到亂咁整<br />\n<br />\n2.效能極低，旗艦機都LAG<br />\n<br />\n3.垃圾廣告message/通知/群組<br />\n<br />\n4.安全性低<br />\n<br />\n5.BUG多到戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n日本人整既hardware我好欣賞，但software就真係不敢恭維"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T12:35:11.000Z","msg":"安全性點低法？係咪又攞返N年前嘅嘢嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426999944b48aec55227ca5ef40e04dab32403e1","tid":578774,"uid":169310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote